{
  "video_id": "2Jhto1-gfMM",
  "title": "Vivo on-screen fingerprint sensor hands-on",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 1139.0,
      "end_time": 3726.0,
      "text": "- Hey, I'm Vlad with The Verge, here at CES 2018."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 3726.0,
      "end_time": 5358.0,
      "text": "And the phone I have in front of me is"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 5358.0,
      "end_time": 7255.0,
      "text": "the first one to have a fingerprint censor"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 7255.0,
      "end_time": 9588.0,
      "text": "integrated into the display."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 10170.0,
      "end_time": 11290.0,
      "text": "And it actually worked."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 11290.0,
      "end_time": 14540.0,
      "text": "(melodic upbeat music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 16215.0,
      "end_time": 18219.0,
      "text": "So this is the first phone to have the fingerprint censor"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 18219.0,
      "end_time": 19990.0,
      "text": "integrated into the display."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 19990.0,
      "end_time": 22587.0,
      "text": "So it's right in this area down here."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 22588.0,
      "end_time": 24749.0,
      "text": "Which is available to use as you would with"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 24749.0,
      "end_time": 26554.0,
      "text": "any other smartphone display."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 26554.0,
      "end_time": 28887.0,
      "text": "But when you lock the phone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 29154.0,
      "end_time": 30525.0,
      "text": "and you want to unlock it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 30525.0,
      "end_time": 32244.0,
      "text": "it turns into a fingerprint sensor."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 32244.0,
      "end_time": 34993.0,
      "text": "It works exactly like the Capacity fingerprint censor"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 34993.0,
      "end_time": 36823.0,
      "text": "you might have seen on Apple iPhone"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 36823.0,
      "end_time": 38882.0,
      "text": "or Samsung Galaxy S-whatever."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 38882.0,
      "end_time": 41251.0,
      "text": "But the difference and the advantage now is that"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 41252.0,
      "end_time": 43282.0,
      "text": "you have these ultra-thin bezels,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 43282.0,
      "end_time": 44803.0,
      "text": "top and bottom on the phone"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 44803.0,
      "end_time": 45971.0,
      "text": "but you still have the fingerprint sensor"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 45972.0,
      "end_time": 47804.0,
      "text": "right at the front where it used to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 47804.0,
      "end_time": 50887.0,
      "text": "And for a lot of people it should be."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 51753.0,
      "end_time": 54840.0,
      "text": "If you have no bezels, you have no where to put it."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 54840.0,
      "end_time": 56652.0,
      "text": "So, a lot of companies had to come up with compromises."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 56652.0,
      "end_time": 58663.0,
      "text": "Samsung's solution was to put it on the back"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 58663.0,
      "end_time": 60541.0,
      "text": "but way over here on the side."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 60541.0,
      "end_time": 62720.0,
      "text": "Which is terrible ergonomically."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 62730.0,
      "end_time": 63564.0,
      "text": "Apple's solution was to just forego"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 63564.0,
      "end_time": 65743.0,
      "text": "Touch ID entirely on the iPhone X."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 65743.0,
      "end_time": 68210.0,
      "text": "Neither of which was really ideal."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 68220.0,
      "end_time": 69619.0,
      "text": "There were many reports that Samsung and Apple"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 69619.0,
      "end_time": 72391.0,
      "text": "were trying to integrate it into the display itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 72391.0,
      "end_time": 73742.0,
      "text": "Under the OLED panel."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 73742.0,
      "end_time": 75800.0,
      "text": "And that's exactly what Vivo has done here"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 75800.0,
      "end_time": 77301.0,
      "text": "with the help with Synaptics."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 77302.0,
      "end_time": 78742.0,
      "text": "Vivo is the first company to introduce this."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 78742.0,
      "end_time": 81446.0,
      "text": "It's very likely that there'll be others following on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 81446.0,
      "end_time": 83149.0,
      "text": "for the rest of the year in 2018."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 83149.0,
      "end_time": 84429.0,
      "text": "And it's really impressive."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 84429.0,
      "end_time": 86520.0,
      "text": "It's exactly, it works exactly as"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 86520.0,
      "end_time": 89600.0,
      "text": "the usual capacative fingerprint sensor does."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 89600.0,
      "end_time": 92980.0,
      "text": "But it's just integrated into the display."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 92990.0,
      "end_time": 93371.0,
      "text": "It feels a little bit magical because"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 93371.0,
      "end_time": 95920.0,
      "text": "you're using the display as you would on any other phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 95920.0,
      "end_time": 97960.0,
      "text": "But when you lock the phone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 97960.0,
      "end_time": 99749.0,
      "text": "and you're trying to unlock it"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 99749.0,
      "end_time": 102589.0,
      "text": "you put your finger on it and it authenticates you."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 102589.0,
      "end_time": 105800.0,
      "text": "It does the usual biometrical authentication."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 105800.0,
      "end_time": 107290.0,
      "text": "It's optical, like the previous stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 107290.0,
      "end_time": 110590.0,
      "text": "Now, this only works with OLED panels because it's optical."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 110590.0,
      "end_time": 112759.0,
      "text": "And there's a synaptics sensor down here at the bottom"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 112760.0,
      "end_time": 114819.0,
      "text": "which looks through the OLED dots."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 114819.0,
      "end_time": 116227.0,
      "text": "This wouldn't work with an LCD"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 116227.0,
      "end_time": 117358.0,
      "text": "because that requires a backlight"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 117358.0,
      "end_time": 119371.0,
      "text": "which would block that recognition."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 119371.0,
      "end_time": 120624.0,
      "text": "So, you will only be able to find this"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 120624.0,
      "end_time": 122220.0,
      "text": "on smartphones with OLED displays"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 122220.0,
      "end_time": 124128.0,
      "text": "coming up in the rest of this year."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 124128.0,
      "end_time": 125528.0,
      "text": "The only difference relative to the usual"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 125528.0,
      "end_time": 126948.0,
      "text": "fingerprint sensors is this one"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 126948.0,
      "end_time": 128467.0,
      "text": "seems to be a little bit slower."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 128467.00000000001,
      "end_time": 129984.00000000001,
      "text": "It isn't quite as lightning-fast as something like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 129985.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132324.0,
      "text": "you would get on the previous iPhones or"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 132324.0,
      "end_time": 134215.0,
      "text": "the OnePlus 5t and so on."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 134215.0,
      "end_time": 135745.0,
      "text": "But it's tolerably slow."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 135745.0,
      "end_time": 138244.0,
      "text": "It's not something that really slows you down."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 138244.0,
      "end_time": 139985.0,
      "text": "Even though it's not terribly well-known globally"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 139985.0,
      "end_time": 141568.0,
      "text": "Vivo is actually one of the world's"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 141568.0,
      "end_time": 142567.0,
      "text": "biggest smartphone manufacturer's."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 142567.0,
      "end_time": 145316.0,
      "text": "Owing to a lot of success in it's native market of China."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 145316.0,
      "end_time": 147268.0,
      "text": "This companies the first to come out with this"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 147268.0,
      "end_time": 150506.0,
      "text": "Synaptics integrated fingerprint sensor solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 150506.0,
      "end_time": 152588.0,
      "text": "But I'm confident that there'll be a whole bunch of others"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 152588.0,
      "end_time": 155716.0,
      "text": "joining it as we go through the year 2018."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 155716.0,
      "end_time": 157916.0,
      "text": "The phone that we're looking at here at CES"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 157916.0,
      "end_time": 159708.0,
      "text": "is very close to the final product."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 159708.0,
      "end_time": 161512.0,
      "text": "It has an aluminum uni-body."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 161512.0,
      "end_time": 163555.0,
      "text": "No fingerprint sensor on the back because obviously"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 163555.0,
      "end_time": 165952.0,
      "text": "it's intgrated into the display itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 165952.0,
      "end_time": 168640.0,
      "text": "I'm liking the fact that it has a headphone jack."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 168640.0,
      "end_time": 169394.0,
      "text": "So, thumbs up for that."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 169395.0,
      "end_time": 171130.0,
      "text": "But I'm noticing right next to the headphone jack"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 171130.0,
      "end_time": 173292.0,
      "text": "is a micro USB port which doesn't make much sense to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 173292.0,
      "end_time": 175532.0,
      "text": "USB-C is the standard of the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 175532.0,
      "end_time": 176365.0,
      "text": "It's reversible."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 176365.0,
      "end_time": 178355.0,
      "text": "It's better in almost every single way."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 178355.0,
      "end_time": 180840.0,
      "text": "And this being Vivo's next flagship"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 180850.0,
      "end_time": 183613.0,
      "text": "and having this brand new, futuristic technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 183613.0,
      "end_time": 186900.0,
      "text": "it makes sense that Vivo would give it"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 186900.0,
      "end_time": 187915.0,
      "text": "the full top-spec treatment."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 187915.0,
      "end_time": 189795.0,
      "text": "So, this might not be the phone you end up buying"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 189795.0,
      "end_time": 191214.0,
      "text": "with a fingerprint sensor integrated"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 191214.0,
      "end_time": 192755.0,
      "text": "directly into this display."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 192755.0,
      "end_time": 194903.0,
      "text": "But I'm confident that the technology itself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 194903.0,
      "end_time": 196405.0,
      "text": "once you try it, is something that"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 196405.0,
      "end_time": 198774.0,
      "text": "a whole bunch of people are going to want and like."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 198774.0,
      "end_time": 201357.0,
      "text": "In part because it's so futuristic feeling."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 201357.0,
      "end_time": 203105.0,
      "text": "It's a technology that used to be"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 203105.0,
      "end_time": 205896.0,
      "text": "on a discreet, separate piece of hardware"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 205896.0,
      "end_time": 207876.0,
      "text": "now integrated directly into the display."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 207877.0,
      "end_time": 211210.0,
      "text": "It's seamless, and it's kinda beautiful."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 212760.0,
      "end_time": 213737.0,
      "text": "So, for more technology like this"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 213737.0,
      "end_time": 215445.0,
      "text": "follow us here on CES 2018"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 215445.0,
      "end_time": 217924.0,
      "text": "on theverge.com and YouTube.com/theverge"
    }
  ]
}